#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:1956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replace <literal>@database</literal> with your tag. Use <literal>\"@*\"</"
"literal> to match the tag against any tag set on the host."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:1960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The activation command matches against <replaceable>VGNAME</replaceable> , "
"<replaceable>VGNAME/LVNAME</replaceable> , or @ <replaceable>TAG</"
"replaceable> set in the metadata of volume groups and logical volumes. A "
"volume group or logical volume is activated only if a metadata tag matches. "
"The default if there is no match, is not to activate."
