#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:1968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <literal>volume_list</literal> is not present and tags are defined on the "
"host, then it activates the volume group or logical volumes only if a host "
"tag matches a metadata tag."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:1973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <literal>volume_list</literal> is defined, but empty, and no tags are "
"defined on the host, then it does not activate."
