#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At start-up, load the <filename>/etc/lvm/lvm.conf</filename> file, and "
"process any tag settings in the file. If any host tags were defined, it "
"loads the related <filename>/etc/lvm/lvm_&lt;<replaceable>HOST_TAG</"
"replaceable>&gt;.conf</filename> file. When it searches for a specific "
"configuration file entry, it searches the host tag file first, then the "
"<filename>lvm.conf </filename> file, and stops at the first match. Within "
"the <filename>lvm_&lt;<replaceable>HOST_TAG</replaceable>&gt;.conf</"
"filename> file, use the reverse order that tags were set in. This allows the "
"file for the last tag set to be searched first. New tags set in the host tag "
