#. Tag: para
#: storage_lvm.xml:2015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set up a simple host name activation control by enabling the "
"<literal>hostname_tags</literal> option in the <filename>/etc/lvm/lvm.conf</"
"filename> file. Use the same file on every machine in a cluster so that it "
"is a global setting."
